      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> - Field 538 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present. If the final
                     subfield is subfield $u, the mark of punctuation precedes that subfield.
      </div>
